dataSource.query:
SELECT
	event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until invoice creation (days)",
    "Time until FI-AR cleared (days)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - FI-AR items created")
        	AS "Time until invoice creation (days)",
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - FI-AR items cleared") 
        	AS "Time until FI-AR cleared (days)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
    GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
